SUMMARY:Thursday Pizza Party
LOCATION:Studio 16
DESCRIPTION:Join us for pizza on Thursday night. Open to all pre-registere
 d attendees\, staff and guests. VIP\, Supporter and Lifetime ticket holder
 s get some extra perks. Listen to Theology and mingle. This event is very 
 friendly to first-time VGM CON attendees! 
END:VEVENT
