SUMMARY:The BGM Run
LOCATION:Key Stage
DESCRIPTION:Kick off your Saturday with an invigorating 4K run\, where eve
 ry step is combined with of your favorite video game music! Join TheToader
  on Saturday\, April 12th\, as we transform the morning into a moving cele
 bration of both fitness and fandom. We’ll gather near the Key Stage at 9
 :45 AM\, ready to embark on our musical journey at 10 AM sharp. 
END:VEVENT
